wiki.content:
year: 2005
 "All About Us" is the first single released from t.A.T.u.'s second English studio album, Dangerous and Moving, and Russian album, Lyudi Invalidy. The song was written by Australian band The Veronicas along with Billy Steinberg and Josh Alexander.
